com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.oldaccounting

Interface OldDataBuilder.IBuildStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OldDataBuilder.AccountGroupStrategy, OldDataBuilder.AccountMapStrategy, OldDataBuilder.AccountStrategy, OldDataBuilder.BalanceStrategy, OldDataBuilder.CapitalEntityStrategy, OldDataBuilder.ItemStrategy, OldDataBuilder.ReimbursementStrategy, OldDataBuilder.TransactionStrategy
    Enclosing class:
    OldDataBuilder

    public static interface OldDataBuilder.IBuildStrategy
    Strategy pattern that allows the Builder to share the basic file-reading code, putting the construction-specific work into each strategy class. Each strategy builds all the data sets that can be built a line at a time. The interface is publicly accessible for unit testing.
